For information about different VAT rates in EU countries, refer to the <a href="https://ec.europa.eu/taxation_customs/economic-analysis-taxation/taxes-europe-database-tedb_en">TEDB ("Taxes in Europe" database)</a>.</p>
</div>
</td>
